{"tid":1418214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家打還打，都要搞清楚目標黎打","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:17:19.000Z","uid":141630,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7de8b4aa7f9dd3d0cbfbf936ad9cb26a94dea8","tid":1418214,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"我知道現場各位手足好燥底<br />\n但記住我地同班狗唔同<br />\n越係燥底就越難保持理智<br />\n唔好好似班狗咁撚樣見人就打<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LaD24ssofh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLaD24ssofh8&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=bc11f3cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LaD24ssofh8</a><br />\n\t<br />\n呢段片未知來龍去脈<br />\n但好影響中立/淺黃嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\n下面係我搵返段立場新聞直播嘅片出黎<br />\n大家唔係有人打你，唔係班黑社會要斬你嘅話，<br />\n最好問清楚咩事先好郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：出核彈我都唔撚割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>北角現場160分個條 1粒鐘09分開車鳩撞</blockquote><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/922200068129837/?t=4136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F922200068129837%2F%3Ft%3D4136&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=c0c2e7ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/922200068129837/?t=4136</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ec6a3a6e9bb7d29ea9a633781da2ba5b4366ffb0","tid":1418214,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"（連仔入）強烈要求取消P牌正負評<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418029</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94fb0bc04d842898c1807b5dd65a43fc564d9157","tid":1418214,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec6a3a6e9bb7d